view.name: Grocery Stores - 2013
view.description: Contains a list of grocery stores which was used by the city to calculate the estimates of Chicagoans living in food deserts in 2013. Data in this file can be cross-referenced with the city's business license data (http://bit.ly/sMFZdN).

columns.name: ACCOUNT NUMBER
columns.description: Account Number is the same as the "Account Number" field in the business license dataset (http://bit.ly/sMFZdN)

columns.name: BUFFER SIZE
columns.description: A binary variable representing the size-of-store. A: 1-mile buffer. B: 0.5 mile buffer
